entries.journal_entry_description: Tulrus are large, dangerous creatures but for the most part they will not attack if unprovoked. The problem is that their numbers are increasing and miners are coming face to face with these beasts more frequently. The numbers of these creatures need to be reduced for safety.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The Tulrus population has obviously gotten out of hand. Too often the miners are coming face to face with these dangerous creatures. It is important that the numbers of Tulrus be reduced.
